  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>디자인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0757ca03-6029-4d59-9c9c-c30cca2358c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a3cd5f1a-77a1-48ca-94ef-7fb910a0640f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fc378dca-000e-4ed8-9d6b-011df2bfb38f\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>진심</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-412a281c-16c5-421f-b445-37d6cc97384f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223808228230/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">가성비가 제일 좋은 택</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>택(Tag)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57cec74-1276-4799-bc79-31936b65d833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 부자재로서 원가에 속하는 인쇄물입니다. 그러므로 가성비가 가장 중요할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44d32905-6eee-4be2-a6f0-d8b32b50a77f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e06b2164-0742-4bc8-a214-b60327182de6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc355143-78b2-4b74-a5a6-c93ae1f07942\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03d0467e-5906-4558-bdd0-c00dedd397b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가성비를 높이는 가장 좋은 방법은 택의 수량을 대량으로 주문하는 것입니다. 이는 500개 주문과 50,000개 주문이 개당 단가가 같을 수 없으므로 다량 주문을 하시면 가성비를 높이는 데 가장 효과적일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69412288-daee-4a0a-ae33-a56e28b8dfbb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7a03486-042a-4d98-84b2-92cc2efd081c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd4162c5-291b-4057-ae2b-72cf2a6053a5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a73d6bd2-b928-4f93-89ea-374ec1bd0564\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 현실적으로는 요즘 트렌드에 맞게 소량으로 주문이 늘고 있어 사실 개당 단가는 높아질 수밖에 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-86aa8bd8-303e-429e-ad52-94c509e82f8e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-572369c7-9fb5-4015-8a2b-9213952b433c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d5abf64-bd17-42fa-8476-dad187f4b9bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d28c47ce-f71c-4a4c-a215-8f6c06c1658e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그럼에도 소량 500개에서 1,000개 사이를 가장 효과적으로 제작하는 방법은 무엇일까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50e05a64-8723-4971-b187-1790f82154b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4415b3c2-b42c-4bce-8f5c-108e7219ce69\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b90308d3-a6d3-4225-8fb9-492c49b3765b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-79e111bc-f58e-4187-9247-e30c4db076bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>가성비 측면</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-01e712b5-d68f-40b7-bd48-4e469676b300\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에서 한번 알아보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-519ec4e9-6c3a-4632-bc04-600275db3066\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-096da162-5d49-47cf-91bf-9431e951c96a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ea3dbf8-6fe0-4e2a-9315-f7f37e05b24a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-29c77b33-7e8b-4b10-a014-6dd9e50c2449\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>행택을 사각형으로 디자인하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2937f41-1a2c-4c3c-a71a-b90d2003c73d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f44ca69-046a-4b97-9b75-31e605ff4c82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb50724f-f919-4eda-9cea-8e0dfbac7577\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-10de67c4-7d33-4c24-b77a-db1313acedc1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반적으로 인쇄에서 사각 재단은 가장 저렴하게 사이즈를 만드는 방법입니다. 흔히 말해 목형을 만들고 도무송(톰슨)으로 제작하게 되면 위와 같은 500개 1,000개 소량 주문은 단가가 비싸질 수밖에 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-992f4a62-9cdb-42d4-8aec-7d996c68e545\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8c75e960-497d-4f72-9b01-367cbe3fe1dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e697cb86-94e1-4fd4-a7bf-a7301179baa2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54b8d37c-99f6-41d4-8441-7419a1ed0fc9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">그러므로 여러분의 회사가 택 단가를 가장 중요하게 생각하신다면 반드시 디자인상 모양을 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-77ba60eb-529f-423b-8889-712ff06e1cb8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>사각형</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1d578f4a-7367-4189-b97e-d59c83333d67\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">으로 제작하시기를 추천드립니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa659071-eeb6-4703-b01c-c4e16753c67a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-959b5381-866e-4357-9ca6-3a5e78a240d9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d84457cb-3923-4cd1-9e33-d5a19c31d99f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39885308-1697-48f5-82ca-9fd6d86dc956\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사각형이 아닌 다른 자유로운 모양의 디자인을 단가가 상승할 수밖에 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c420373-de34-41b3-b531-43e65b4cbd8d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c5a92d3-2f8b-402d-9ac3-7f0ab31d85ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14e3356c-b93e-4d42-b972-1d2a635a37f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d882d3a0-5530-43f4-a1a6-bb59edc990cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8fce2153-4987-40c1-a454-947744eb35f2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f210cd88-adf7-419d-b822-a7f2bdf4da61\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>그리고 타공 외에 다른 후공정을 작업하지 마십시오.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-87fa9960-f63f-4e10-8942-0742efc7c980\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1e59ffa-ef7a-4c65-b0f9-e8138beff472\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6153e962-15e5-4638-b744-28b3b14ab4b2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eb555510-d527-415f-923a-84f1f7e85cbe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">택에서 가장 단가 상승 요인이 큰 것이 후공정입니다. 박인쇄나 형압 등을 넣으면 단가는 상승할 수밖에 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0deaa8df-941f-4aff-b2e2-798b9ce6dfe0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-44137aba-ace9-4066-9f30-20790a895cae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 접거나 중간에 누름선(오시)같은 작업이 들어가면 당연히 단가는 상승합니다. 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8ceb3ed-799c-4c03-8b72-c9fbb26f8812\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d5d5352c-82eb-4035-81b5-786fbae94ab2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d60a57df-d835-4394-b789-fa7c20dec277\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2dccf3e3-c57a-487a-8963-bb1e02cccdd6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이렇듯 그냥 일반적인 스노우지에 사각형으로 앞면 컬러 뒷면 먹 1도로 타공만 뚫어서 생산하면 아마도 가장 저렴하게 택을 작업하시는 것일 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-691b2794-6745-41da-8176-f2a01acb31d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f47c602d-167f-446d-b288-e2aa2abdc84c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71ccea60-b3bc-4e8a-be7e-9d49fe12f307\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3d65e995-a8f7-4720-8ef5-078f938e9d2c\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>*주의사항</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dc8b6c5e-e561-48d8-b174-02df6e68c746\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81a00ced-8dc6-423b-a9d1-82b11a50ca11\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">재단과 타공으로만 이루어지므로 보통의 목형과 도무송(톰슨)보다는 따지는 부분보다 간격이나 정밀도에서 약간의 차이가 발생될 수 있습니다. 그리고 수량도 500매 정매 생산이 안될 수 있으니 이점 참고하시기 바랍니다. 이유는 단가를 위해 합판 인쇄가 이루어질 수 있기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line3\" id=\"SE-f6434c2e-71cb-44ae-8be9-5a8d213451b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line3 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a4f051e9-63e6-4328-b02a-b1c1840cd8d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bf02ab69-9560-43e8-9bbf-1e3e4fe2b7bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fdc94be8-e790-493c-8120-78c9c279549f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>가장 저렴한 택 사양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d9faa819-be51-4478-9480-ba1123ddbfbd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-485227e1-d2e9-4fad-b77e-afe9d34f4e1f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6870f7df-9da5-49fb-a5f8-a4c12b58e726\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f67a5245-2102-43df-97c3-55964c34ba40\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 : 아트지/스노우지 계열</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-73eb835d-10ba-4218-83a1-217fcd63716a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3d3f50aa-dac1-4fe3-a49c-de44b76ae439\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈 : 명함 9cm × 5cm보다 작은 사이즈</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cec45bf5-0a80-43d4-8c77-a1f38775c71a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-59e27bcc-2420-4992-9c95-8874907503d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 : 앞면 컬러 + 뒷면 먹</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb537b97-b66a-466c-9960-7566b0686b50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fcfe9e1-dbfa-49d9-88a2-d033912e4ddb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후공정 : 사각 재단 + 타공 1개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bcba1b7a-df3b-4919-a72e-4345deace715\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f495d743-b2b4-45bc-9e2b-c364d91c88ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b08880bc-e654-4647-a330-42aef295facc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2d99e05-3c8d-4e3c-91cb-94d929763521\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">이렇게 작업하면 500개 정도는 거의 몇만 원밖에 단가가 나오지 않을 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d27942f4-d7cc-4724-92b1-9de741a02fe9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-615f7692-78bd-451c-bf1a-5d868387b937\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-910e311c-25ce-4dc5-a10a-661ac4617b06\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef509aa4-75d8-41aa-aa0f-ad90c57d9434\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-87c33b06-6f51-40cf-aa6e-c27027509ac7\" style=\"\">퀄리티가 제일 좋아 보이는 택</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-237ec6a3-8834-45d1-9a24-955e1b4bcb68\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b598bb2-f9b6-4c38-a896-fb8fbf6a7d09\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-54a23c21-8cca-4eab-8159-0fe2aa11ed34\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>퀄리티</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8ca18e9-0b6d-4008-9edd-c4791ff7e171\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는 보는 사람마다 판단이 다르지만 일반적으로 택에서 퀄리티 있어 보이는 쪽은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3489c1fc-cb0b-4688-b569-4f8a7bbfce87\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>모양택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-30a17118-e4d1-46bd-a6a9-73fc65305520\" style=\"color:#555555;\">들입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9ef332d6-6c85-4c94-b486-c99a1471c17b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223808228230/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da36cece-d38d-4edf-93f0-3bc9c9a3d2ee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d52310f7-47bb-4983-9179-d02556341852\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ca4bd121-63c3-4cf1-91a9-56d7d7193ea2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량이지만 제품 하나하나에 품격을 높이기 위해서 브랜드와 맞는 컬러의 색지를 사용하였으며 본 내용은 백색 인쇄로 그 품격을 더했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a0c40eda-bfcf-43fc-9411-22709854d74d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-801c6443-4085-4393-8b6a-1a16a245c1cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 금별색으로 로고를 디자인할 수 있고 상단에 아일렛으로 택의 타공부분을 보호했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-61f8401b-5b27-4cda-8756-9754db30b013\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f651a07-7748-417a-9ee5-1e349886cbb9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca9b3d93-b3a8-4f29-a005-a7a554e940e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56efcab6-e63e-4e8d-aa1c-1fa84db11375\" style=\"color:#555555;\">택의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ffc78493-0692-4ef8-936d-c47610d0bb6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>퀄리티 측면</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-364b2f4e-2598-4941-b0b3-09f94687f395\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에서 한번 알아보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3d4192d-da55-48a2-b96c-82dc8a02f4f6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba303510-28d7-4e6f-bee4-9687958ffc36\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-93ab6fb1-6f4c-4a04-9079-c05a92bed253\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0457475b-7ec8-4361-b4f8-578a60df96de\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>행택을 자유로운 모양으로 만드세요. 그러면 더 브랜드에 맞는 디자인으로 제작할 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ae627c0-f603-43aa-b6ad-49539e5c07c2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2ca1aa3-d505-414e-9947-0e938626158e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3acc6101-28f9-4cdd-a361-d5093761efba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-473ae611-bfdf-4e47-8db3-7f86ea047bb0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">재단 방법이 아닌 도무송을 하면 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-03edcdde-b568-46fd-a124-47294c6bd6fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>자유롭게 커팅 하여</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-831cdbe0-8c54-4171-a749-423e9b147051\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 정확하게 모양을 딸 수 있습니다. 물론 이 부분도 제약사항이 있지만 일반 재단보다는 더 정밀하게 디자인 대로 생산되어 나옵니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2e70aad0-1b05-48dd-8882-1e7f0e913d2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0be55337-9e8c-4199-8347-351d824cf905\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc45edcf-391e-43e5-add9-197b40c228d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8c34d456-bdff-44f0-8502-98424ab8b0e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그런 이유로 고품격의 행택들은 거의 자유로운 모양으로 제작되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae16eecf-e0a4-4413-b108-4e1fc413cb9b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ff68ded-0a10-4a4e-941b-6e2a7c8393ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a93dd27-c031-4259-9e8c-925e06d6168a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cc3c68d8-dfc6-41bd-bfe1-64761167b21f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f98c241-035a-45ca-9e22-cb8cdc146bfd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a5391d0b-939f-4754-b43b-d226afdad361\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이를 브랜드에 맞게 선택하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2f7f879-f2a5-49fb-b3a8-9add385d8f32\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-339452ac-2eb5-4807-945f-808b6f748294\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b29f83f-66c8-4df2-aca6-f5c1ba66ebb0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6aced33-ff98-474c-b13d-25af1fc69ff5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여러분의 제품이 친환경에 가깝다면 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f517a53b-7634-4167-847f-caa27b0df3a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>크라프트지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-83e00297-b31a-4e93-9242-d8876f9503d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">나 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b95bd6fe-ffde-4d7c-ac6a-cc05350829f2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>친환경 종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ea353d9-5fe1-4be4-9099-4795aa161486\" style=\"color:#555555;\">를 사용하실 수 있습니다. 이미 요즘은 너무나도 다양한 종이가 생산되고 있습니다. 미팅을 통해 자신의 브랜드에 맞는 종이를 선택하세요. 그러면 인쇄로 브랜드 색상을 맞추는 것보다 더 통일되고 일관적으로 색감이 표현될 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ef91721-eb1c-4a0a-a8ac-33fa1bb24d0d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bbe1c3f6-b85a-45d2-b576-32ee44cdcb54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a56fd402-3d0c-4bd9-8781-9ae320b6d8fd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03606961-df4f-4d87-8151-fc030c52f9b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">예를 들어 검은 색지에 백색 인쇄하는 것도 좋은 방법 중에 하나입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02b8ce08-143c-427a-9d60-98ee09e2def2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223808228230/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a6bd818-256d-4061-8063-283e5f16ef92\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c2a1b97-5553-4869-88fc-a986e681b0c0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5d5528dd-ce0b-43f0-bcf0-3ec0ef67572b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1ab90105-a4f8-4c33-bbb2-498667305280\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e005231-b5d4-4d77-a1d1-34603db5430c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-acf53d73-4c8d-4832-9e90-6a2a8d3ce01c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-11a0071c-f0f6-4984-8821-08d91ebf17fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다양한 후공정으로 퀄리티를 높이세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65e6f887-5c32-42ea-97db-ce3978c5521c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54d8cb06-967f-4164-9a44-1e023d42bf87\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f93ca4ef-5055-47a5-9f03-148c830110c5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fd06cd1c-6f02-4a9a-89b2-2fabbe4b1265\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후공정은 너무도 다양합니다. 박인쇄, 형압, 접지, 코팅, 에폭시 등 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf2d4746-3775-476a-b741-9f0baa907c53\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8932722-d1e2-4d95-bdc7-cb00d426bd97\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자신의 브랜드에 맞는 후공정을 선택하여 가장 퀄리티 높은 택을 생산해 보세요. 제품을 받은 고객이 버리기 아까운 택이야말로 제품을 부연 설명하는 말이 필요 없는 부자재가 될 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2974d900-5ff2-4308-bd5f-cb62d624b8fa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b5f0520-b89a-49f7-b78c-fff3f0840730\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ad1fd13-8027-476c-98e3-7cf0bdbe66c4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3bc5325a-c74e-4133-b99f-e90a3f9f480e\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>*주의사항</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e7a481a2-b6dd-4b77-bf03-3735a5358ed1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24f68fa7-202a-4b5e-8c6e-bd77116284af\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">퀄리티를 높이는 것은 좋지만 원가에 속하는 부자재의 단가를 무시하고 진행할 수는 없으실 겁니다. 그러므로 반드시 발주처와 상의하여 가장 효과적인 방법을 찾으셔야 할 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f74dae7d-2277-470c-9653-6b4b7187fc46\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99ac1fe2-d743-43ad-bd4a-ddafd224f39b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e36cd74-10d5-4fd0-9132-1b3041c664da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05e59eca-f7a7-4b53-96a4-504a1c49f2b6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">그렇지 않으면 자칫 돈만 낭비하는 결과가 초래될 수 있습니다. 잘 판단하시고 주문하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8d77a3f7-dbcf-4a44-933c-783513c99428\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b32bee24-6a43-4e35-865e-e6b9e8f5b7b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-39962aa8-306e-4a62-94cb-ee7f69723b9b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2d893385-49fc-4a1a-883e-69df34d2ae16\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니은 항상 고객의 성공과 함께합니다. 언제든 질문의 문은 활짝 열어 놓겠습니다. 톡톡이나 전화 주시면 친절하게 안내드리겠습니다. 감사합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3bc32fbd-e2dd-4571-ad02-a72daadb3c58\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-140f2eb4-f193-4a1c-86cc-b43051da0b62\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc4d495b-3445-407c-9353-78d0f4366746\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223808228230/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b59d06b9-9a1f-4e19-9bdb-fbf036ad4f2f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223808228230/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e3ef242f-4606-4d9c-9abc-2cfc4e95f5a1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e33757ef-614e-46f4-8ee5-b211f6b2b631\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2fa3b49e-fd2c-4b0d-af46-2e11185b43e6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56c4cbb8-ecca-430c-a69a-a95e8dc37064\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}